          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1708093485226-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a separate large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced spring greens </strong>with the <strong>remaining chopped garlic & ginger</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 3-4 min or until tender with a bite – these are your <strong>garlic & ginger greens</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1708093489949-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1708093489949-x400.jpg",
