          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1708093489949-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the the sauce has thickened, transfer the <strong>cooked pork loin steak[s] </strong>to the pan with any <strong>cooking juices</strong> and reduce the heat to very low until ready to serve – this is your <strong>Goan-style vindaloo pork</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1708093525147-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
