            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Goan-style vindaloo pork</strong> with the <strong>curried potatoes</strong> and <strong>garlic & ginger greens </strong>to the side</p><p>Drizzle over any <strong>remaining Goan-style vindaloo curry sauce</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
